{
  "id": "RAW_094287",
  "title": "大模型的未来，是 Agent 还是 App？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/5JzhJIUY3vpz4RGyobI7Ag",
  "date": "2025-03-08 13:57:43",
  "author": "orangesai",
  "siteName": "有机大橘子",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">导读：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI 说 Deep Research 其实是</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">模型，它基于 o3 训练，但不是 o3 加一堆工作流。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic 对 Agent 的定义是：</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent 必须在内部执行目标任务，而不是依赖外部的工作流。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在强化学习时代，给模型一个封闭的环境和奖励，模型就可以学会这个环境的生存法则。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">强化学习可以让大模型+工作流真正变为内化的 Agent，完成端到端的任务。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">如果模型公司已经可以完成端到端任务，是不是模型本身就是应用？</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">那应用公司的空间是否依然存在？这个问题值得思考。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">本文部分摘录并翻译自 Alexander Doria，一家正在做 RAG Agent 的联创。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">摘录开始：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <hr style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;border-width:1px 0px 0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-style:solid;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在过去几周，我们看到了\"模型作为产品\"的两个典型例子：OpenAI 的 Deep Research 和 Claude Sonnet 3.7。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">我读到很多关于 Deep Research 的误解，这些误解因开源和闭源克隆产品的增多而更加严重。OpenAI 并非仅在 O3 之上构建了一个包装器。他们</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 109, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">训练了一个全新的模型</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">，能够在内部执行搜索，无需任何外部调用、提示或编排：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;padding:0px 4px 0px 12px;color:rgb(89, 89, 89);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">深度研究模型由针对网页浏览优化的早期版本 OpenAI o3 提供支持。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">该模型学习了核心浏览能力（搜索、点击、滚动、解析文件）（...），并通过对这些浏览任务的强化学习训练，学会了如何推理以综合大量网站信息，找到特定内容或编写全面报告。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">Deep Research 不是标准的 LLM，也不是普通的聊天机器人。它是一种新型的\"研究语言模型\"，专门设计用于端到端执行搜索任务。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">对于认真使用它的人来说，这种差异立即显现：该模型能生成结构连贯、具有系统化源分析过程的长篇报告。相比之下，正如 Hanchung Lee&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 109, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">指出的</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">，其他所有的 Deep Search，包括 Perplexity 和 Google 的变体，都只是带有一些微调的常规模型：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;padding:0px 4px 0px 12px;color:rgb(89, 89, 89);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">Google 的 Gemini 和 Perplexity 的聊天助手也提供\"深度研究\"功能，但它们都没有发布任何关于如何为此任务优化模型或系统的文献，也没有进行任何实质性的定量评估（...）我们假设它们所做的微调工作并不显著。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic 一直在更清晰地阐述他们的愿景。去年十二月，他们提出了一个有争议但在我看来正确的 Agent&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 109, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">模型定义</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">类似于 Deep Search，Agent 必须在内部执行目标任务：它们\"动态指导自己的过程和工具使用，控制完成任务的方式\"。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">目前大多数 Agent 初创公司构建的不是真正的 Agent，而是工作流，即\"通过预定义的代码路径编排 LLM 和工具的系统\"。工作流在某些垂直领域仍可能创造价值。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">然而，对于现在在大型实验室工作的人来说，显而易见的是，自主系统的所有重大进展都将首先通过重新设计模型来实现。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude 3.7 的发布就是一个非常具体的例证，这个模型主要是为处理复杂代码用例而训练的。所有类似 Devin 的工作流调整在软件工程基准测试中都获得了显著提升。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">再举一个小规模的例子：在 Pleias，我们目前正致力于 RAG 的自动化。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">当前的 RAG 系统由许多相互关联但脆弱的工作流组成：路由、分块、重排序、查询解释、查询扩展、源上下文化和搜索工程。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">随着训练技术栈的发展，有可能将所有这些流程整合到两个独立但相互关联的模型中：一个用于数据准备，另一个用于搜索/检索/报告生成。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">这需要精心设计的合成流程和全新的强化学习奖励函数。真正的训练，真正的研究。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">这在实践中意味着：转移复杂性。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">训练预先考虑了各种行动和边缘情况，使部署变得更简单。但在这个过程中，大部分价值现在由模型训练者创造，最终也可能被他们获取。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">简而言之，Claude 的目标是颠覆并取代当前的工作流，比如来自 llama index 的这种基本\"代理\"系统：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100001784\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/911ee685-3676-4d0f-7bbd-aa60118ba400/public\" data-type=\"png\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 12px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/911ee685-3676-4d0f-7bbd-aa60118ba400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">替换为这样：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100001785\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/435efe41-5ad8-40e4-6cab-9398a9b29800/public\" data-type=\"png\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 12px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/435efe41-5ad8-40e4-6cab-9398a9b29800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <hr style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;border-width:1px 0px 0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-style:solid;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">摘录完毕。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">原文还有一些激进的观点，认为模型公司在未来的几年将会吞噬应用公司，并会停止像应用公司提供 API。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">这个问题有点类似于：如果利润足够丰厚，DeepSeek 还会继续开源吗？</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">此事有关信仰，在此不做过多引述，可自行阅读。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 109, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: #000;\">https://vintagedata.org/blog/posts/model-is-the-product</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\">　</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-styl